{"tid":1323034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六月內地訪港旅行團未因修例爭議減少","createTime":"2019-07-16T06:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T10:40:31.000Z","uid":36563,"like":60,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0d69a1292c007397578022253ff69ab64bdd0bc9","tid":1323034,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:18:25.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】旅遊業議會表示，上月內地訪港旅行團的數字，未有因為逃犯條例修訂爭議而減少。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊業議會回覆本台查詢時指，今年六月有5641個內地旅行團來港，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>比去年六月增加約兩成三</strong></span></span>，至於今年上半年，一共有39332團來港，較去年同期上升約三成四。議會仍在統計七月初的數據，暫時未能提供。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Tm6rQjPCkjs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTm6rQjPCkjs&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=2b27b9fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Tm6rQjPCkjs</a><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=355576&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355576%26refer%3DShare&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=aab5958b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355576%26refer%3DShare&h=c88d971b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=355576&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保皇黨不如出嚟講返兩句？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c1eb9752a4063923b770fc2653eb2775f5e8db","tid":1323034,"uid":36563,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"示威活動刺激本港旅遊業，從而推動香港經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府可能發現左示威活動係香港新景點，<br />\n所以先冇諗住停<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲諗住繼續搞大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf16d9103d9332dcb758c1053f524887e0cb09c",